I"<	<p><strong><em>Meny’Umuganda</em></strong></p>

<p>Umuganda ukorwa buri kwezi, ugateganywa n’itegeko 53/… 2009. N’ubwo ukunze kugendera ku mateka n’amabwiriza y’ibiro bya “Prime minister” uyoborwa umunsi kuwundi n’abakozi benshi bari mu matsinda y’inzego z’abayobozi (Steering Commitees) n’izabakozi basanzwe (Techinical Committees) barimo aba leta n’abandi. Reba anabwiriza abiteganya.
Kugeza ubu…</p>

<p><strong>Ibyiciro by’Umuganda</strong></p>
<ol>
  <li>Ibitekerezo, Udushya n’Ubuhanzi…</li>
  <li>Umuganda Usanzwe</li>
  <li>Ibikorwa by’Imishinga y’Imihigo</li>
  <li>Ibikorwa by’Abaturiye Umudugudu Bitegurira Bakanasoza</li>
  <li>Umuganda w’Abanyamyuga Bishyize Hamwe</li>
  <li>Impano z’Ibikorwaremezo, Ibintu, Amafaranga…</li>
  <li>Ikoranabuhanga Ryimbitse</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Amatsinda mu Muganda</strong>
Ni byiza ko mbere yo gutoranya ikyiciro wakoreramo umuganda, utoranya itsinda rikubereye ukurije ubushobozi, umwuga, inararibonye, yewe n’uko wibona mw’itsinda ririho, cyangwa ririkuremwa. Amatsinda ashoboka ni nka:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Imiryango, Ibigo, Leta… n’abandi Bafitiye Ubushobozi</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ubucuruzi n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri ya ICT, Guhanga udushya n’abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ingabo n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ubuzima n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Uburinganire n’Iterambere ry’Umurango n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri ya Siporo n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri Ishinzwe Imicungire Yihutirwa n’Ibiza n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri mu Biro bya Perezida n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Inzegozibanze n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Imari, n’Igenamigambi ry’Ubukungu n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ibikorwaremezo n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ibidukikije n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ubuhinzi n’Amatungo n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Uburezi n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Urubyiruko n’Umuco n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Minisiteri y’Ubutabera n’Abafatanyabikorwa Babo</li>
  <li>Mini</li>
</ol>

<p>Ibitekerezo, udushya n’ubuhanzi</p>
